@startuml
state "Order" as Order
state "Arrival" as Arrival
state "Preparation" as Preparation
state "Operations" as Operations
state "Maintenance" as Maintenance

[*] --> Order : newly acquired plane
Order --> Arrival : plane arrives
Arrival --> Preparation : transition to preparation
Preparation --> Operations : assigned to operations or maintenance based on condition and schedule
Operations --> Maintenance : no more scheduled flights or maintenance required
Maintenance --> Preparation : after checking and servicing
Order --> [*] : permanently withdrawn from service

@enduml
